From there, the team touch base with a rough and tumble businessman who brings bespoke adventure experiences to life. programme.title: Country Ball

Why? Because despite his athletic and academic prowess, Kayleb has one arm. programme.title: Surviving Mann

As Don Mann continues to forge a battle-ready team, the squad is thrown into breaching drills designed for high-stakes mission execution.
